long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A simple chromium extension designed to autocomplete EDClub exercises for you.

You may adjust the autocompletion speed, the speed variability and even chance of making a mistake and the time it takes to correct from the mistake in the popup menu.

Autocompletion can be toggled using the F8 key.
